properties.Tooltip Notes: Minimum lot depth 100 ft for single-unit residences; 150ft for 2+ unit residences. Maximum accessory dwelling unit height 24 ft. A variety of density bonuses are available for PUDs that have applicable units (affordable or workforce housing, housing for the elderly or people with disabilities) or that meet certain environmental standards (LEED certification or alternative energy efficiency standard). Bonuses are scaled based on the extent to which these initiatives are met. Bonuses may not be combined.
